with this syntax.
It means :

97
00:05:15,496 --> 00:05:18,097
the "compteur" variable,
of the "Rectangle" class,

98
00:05:18,097 --> 00:05:19,417
of the integer type,

99
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:21,360
will be initialized to 0.

100
00:05:22,009 --> 00:05:23,979
Such a line of code will appear

101
